---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Pest Control Cairns Region | Full Coverage"
  description="Pest control across the Cairns region — northern beaches to Gordonvale, valley to coast. General pest, termites, cockroaches, ants, rodents and commercial. AS 3660, APVMA-registered, free quote."
  canonical="https://cairnspestmanagement.com.au/cairns-region/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Cairns region &middot; full coverage</span>
      <h1>Pest control across the <span class="accent">Cairns region</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From the northern beaches down to Gordonvale, rainforest valley to coast,
        homes to commercial premises. One wet-tropics climate, several different
        pest pictures &mdash; and we work all of them, every week.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured suburb pages.</h3>
        <p>Each with local pest context &mdash; the housing mix, the dominant pests, and how the tropical climate plays out street by street.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/edmonton/">Edmonton</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/smithfield/">Smithfield</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/redlynch/">Redlynch</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/trinity-beach/">Trinity Beach</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/earlville/">Earlville</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Other Cairns suburbs we cover.</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cairns City</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Mooroobool</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Gordonvale</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Palm Cove</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Clifton Beach</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Kewarra Beach</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Westcourt</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Manunda</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bayview Heights</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Mount Sheridan</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bentley Park</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">White Rock</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Brinsmead</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Whitfield</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bungalow</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Parramatta Park</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Woree</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Trinity Park</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Holloways Beach</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Machans Beach</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Yorkeys Knob</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Aeroglen</span>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Several pest pictures across the region.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Northern beaches</strong> (Trinity Beach, Palm Cove, Clifton
          Beach, Kewarra Beach): holiday-let and rental turnover keeps cockroach,
          ant and mosquito pressure high, with coastal homes also needing rodent
          and termite cover. Fast turnaround and recurring plans suit hosts here.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Rainforest valley</strong> (Redlynch, Brinsmead, Whitfield):
          backing onto World Heritage rainforest and the ranges, this is the
          highest natural pest-pressure pocket of Cairns &mdash; very active
          termites, a strong wet-season rodent push, and year-round cockroaches and
          ants in the lush gardens.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Southern growth corridor</strong> (Edmonton, Mount Sheridan,
          Bentley Park, Gordonvale): new estates and established homes side by
          side, both fighting year-round cockroaches and ants, with new builds
          needing annual termite inspections to keep their barrier warranties valid.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Inner-city and commercial</strong> (Cairns City, Earlville,
          Bungalow, Portsmith, Westcourt): retail strips, cafes, offices and unit
          complexes that run documented commercial and body-corporate programs
          alongside everyday residential treatments.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Why year-round protection matters in the tropics.</h3>
        <p>
          The single thing that sets Cairns apart is that pests never get a winter
          knock-back. Cockroaches, ants and mosquitoes breed continuously, the wet
          season drives rodents indoors, and termites &mdash; both Coptotermes and
          the giant northern Mastotermes &mdash; stay active all year. A one-off
          treatment clears what is there now but gets re-colonised within weeks,
          which is why most homes and every commercial site do best on a
          <strong>recurring plan</strong>. All our work is carried out by a
          licensed Queensland Pest Management Technician using APVMA-registered
          products, and our termite work follows AS&nbsp;3660.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five services</span>
      <h2>What we do.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/general-pest-control/"><h3>General pest control</h3><p>Cockroaches, ants, spiders, silverfish. 12-month warranty. From ~$250.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/termite-control/"><h3>Termite inspections &amp; treatment</h3><p>AS 3660 inspections, Termidor barriers, Sentricon baiting. From ~$235.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/cockroach-ant-control/"><h3>Cockroach &amp; ant control</h3><p>Gel and residual treatment, species-matched. Warranty-backed.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/rodent-control/"><h3>Rodent control</h3><p>Rat and mouse baiting, proofing, roof-void treatment. From ~$180.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/commercial-pest-control/"><h3>Commercial pest control</h3><p>HACCP-aligned programs for cafes, body-corp and rentals. Per site.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free pest control quote anywhere in the Cairns region.</h2>
        <p>Northern beaches, valley, southern corridor or inner city. Homes and commercial. Recurring plans available.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
